title: Marta Tejedor
text:
Marta Tejedor Munuera (born 23 December 1968) is a Spanish <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Coach%20%28sports%29">coach</a> who most recently managed <a href="Birmingham%20City%20W.F.C.">Birmingham City</a> of the <a href="FA%20Women%27s%20Super%20League">FA Women's Super League</a>.
She had also coached the women's national teams of <a href="Chile%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Chile</a> and <a href="Peru%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Peru</a>.
